The paper deals with privacy protection in street-view images, which involves computer vision techniques such as object segmentation and inpainting. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves depth estimation and multi-view imagery, which are related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, privacy protection is a security concern, which could fall under the sub-categories of cryptography (cs.CR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
